Listen.
- I can't hear anything.

22
00:04:41,142 --> 00:04:43,462
I think there's a problem with
the differential.

23
00:04:44,204 --> 00:04:47,454
I'll check it in the garage.
- Sure. - Okay.

24
00:04:49,787 --> 00:04:52,287
