"Wish this car belonged to me."

734
01:22:58,107 --> 01:23:00,065
"I would've had children and wife."

735
01:23:00,482 --> 01:23:03,481
"Wish this car belonged to me."

736
01:23:03,731 --> 01:23:06,981
"I would've had children and wife."

737
01:23:07,064 --> 01:23:14,333
"It is nothing about me,
but their night would be theirs."

738
01:23:14,697 --> 01:23:16,724
"Why are you crying? Hit the hammer."

739
01:23:17,085 --> 01:23:20,938
"This is a car worth 5 lakhs."

740
01:23:21,021 --> 01:23:25,478
"This is a car worth 5 lakhs."

741
01:23:25,687 --> 01:23:30,520
"I don't know what the problem is.
A palace is standing above the house."

742
01:23:30,979 --> 01:23:33,936
"I don't know what the problem is."

743
01:23:34,019 --> 01:23:37,519
"A palace is standing
above the house."

744
01:23:37,603 --> 01:23:43,768
"Uncle is dying of hunger and
the rich man's warehouse is full."

745
01:23:44,268 --> 01:23:47,476
"Tell me if anyone knows."

746
01:23:47,560 --> 01:23:49,935
"What the problem is?"

747
01:23:50,018 --> 01:23:52,226
"What the problem is?"

748
01:23:52,310 --> 01:23:57,184
"You, you, you, you!
May be even he doesn't know."

749
01:23:57,684 --> 01:23:59,976
"What the problem is?"

750
01:24:00,059 --> 01:24:02,267
"What the problem is?"

751
01:24:06,558 --> 01:24:10,975
"This is a car worth 5 lakhs."

752
01:24:12,932 --> 01:24:21,631
"It runs..
car too.. his and mine too."

753
01:24:21,682 --> 01:24:26,606
"If it runs, it is light..
but the car is heavy."

754
01:24:30,723 --> 01:24:34,972
"This is a car worth 5 lakhs."

755
01:24:35,055 --> 01:24:39,180
"This is a car worth 5 lakhs."

756
01:24:39,263 --> 01:24:43,304
"This is a car worth 5 lakhs."

757
01:26:06,747 --> 01:26:09,421
Dominic, finally today
I am able to meet you.

758
01:26:11,280 --> 01:26:16,065
I am of course a priest,
but am your friend too.

759
01:26:17,680 --> 01:26:21,555
I want to help you. Do you agree?

760
01:26:23,241 --> 01:26:28,086
I will help you, but I need your help.

761
01:26:29,805 --> 01:26:31,117
My help?

762
01:26:31,168 --> 01:26:35,765
Yes, your help
so that I can help you.

763
01:26:37,439 --> 01:26:39,256
Can we meet once a week?

764
01:26:41,037 --> 01:26:43,465
Oh! What's the matter?

765
01:26:45,292 --> 01:26:48,250
What happened?
Nothing, my shirt tore.

766
01:26:48,421 --> 01:26:49,421
How?

767
01:26:50,198 --> 01:26:52,740
Goons.. they had come
to call off the strike.

768
01:26:54,154 --> 01:26:55,914
Good evening, Father.
- Good evening.

769
01:26:55,965 --> 01:26:58,857
How are you?
-I am alright, but are you hurt?

770
01:26:59,100 --> 01:27:02,464
He is of course hurt.
I will get hot water for you.

771
01:27:02,661 --> 01:27:05,433
No need.. this has just began..

772
01:27:06,839 --> 01:27:10,339
For now, I have just been slapped
and threatened.

773
01:27:12,303 --> 01:27:14,097
We'll get to see
much worse ahead.

774
01:27:21,081 --> 01:27:23,985
Father, can you help my father?

775
01:27:27,753 --> 01:27:30,895
What can I do? This is bloodshed.

776
01:27:31,603 --> 01:27:34,971
Who will explain to these heartless?
Who will stop this rioting?

777
01:27:35,211 --> 01:27:38,141
What can we do when everyone
has become each other's enemy?

778
01:27:39,094 --> 01:27:40,552
There's hatred everywhere.

779
01:27:42,267 --> 01:27:44,509
There's nothing like love and peace.

780
01:27:45,197 --> 01:27:46,613
What can anyone do?

781
01:27:47,476 --> 01:27:48,696
We can fight.

782
01:27:49,032 --> 01:27:52,758
No. No one has benefited
by fighting. Never.

783
01:27:57,752 --> 01:28:02,288
My father was thrashed yesterday.

784
01:28:06,622 --> 01:28:11,548
Not very badly,
but he was humiliated.

785
01:28:16,696 --> 01:28:18,113
He is really hurt.

786
01:28:21,623 --> 01:28:24,680
My father never harmed anyone,

787
01:28:24,730 --> 01:28:27,333
but even so, why did this happen to him?

788
01:28:30,053 --> 01:28:31,678
Goons thrashed him.

789
01:28:33,841 --> 01:28:35,841
What do the goons
have to do with strike?

790
01:28:39,380 --> 01:28:42,474
Albert, do you remember
I had told you..

791
01:28:42,662 --> 01:28:44,935
..that the result of
a challenge is fighting?

792
01:28:45,410 --> 01:28:47,276
Do you remember?
- Yes.

793
01:28:47,749 --> 01:28:49,274
Look, now you are very stressed.

794
01:28:50,159 --> 01:28:53,327
When you have cooled down,
we'll talk about this.

795
01:28:55,124 --> 01:29:00,916
Sir.. my father is
a very kind-hearted man.

796
01:29:03,130 --> 01:29:06,297
He is a very simple man.
He's never harmed anyone.

797
01:29:07,868 --> 01:29:09,285
He only demanded his rights.

798
01:29:10,821 --> 01:29:13,569
If anyone demands rights,
do they have to humiliated?

799
01:29:15,159 --> 01:29:16,851
You are telling the same thing again.

800
01:29:16,902 --> 01:29:20,402
See, has anyone got
anything with a strike?

801
01:29:21,291 --> 01:29:22,790
You don't get it?
Do you?

802
01:29:24,167 --> 01:29:27,801
This is a serious issue.
This is a very complex matter.

803
01:29:28,749 --> 01:29:31,984
One day when you are calmer,
we will surely talk about it, okay?

804
01:29:32,071 --> 01:29:33,904
Okay?
- But.. sir..

805
01:29:34,067 --> 01:29:37,567
For now, you should
go home and take rest.

806
01:29:44,384 --> 01:29:48,102
And yes, convince your father
not to get entangled in strike and all.

807
01:29:49,129 --> 01:29:51,628
Only goons and hoodlums do this.

808
01:29:52,768 --> 01:29:53,768
Got it?

809
01:30:00,497 --> 01:30:01,829
I shall leave.

810
01:30:11,646 --> 01:30:13,146
Help us!

811
01:30:13,438 --> 01:30:15,867
Help us, give us bread
for the ones in trouble.

812
01:30:23,520 --> 01:30:26,999
Help us!
Give us roti, give us roti.

813
01:31:05,558 --> 01:31:07,872
Yes.. we are here from Bharat News.

814
01:31:08,922 --> 01:31:11,908
To ask our labour comrades
about the strike.

815
01:31:12,158 --> 01:31:14,685
We have to ask few
questions about the strike.

816
01:31:15,683 --> 01:31:19,297
Our strike is going on..
it is absolutely going on!

817
01:31:19,995 --> 01:31:23,495
To break the strike, the owners
are sending goons and hoodlums.

818
01:31:24,235 --> 01:31:27,407
The owner cannot break the
strike by sending goons and hoodlums.

819
01:31:28,636 --> 01:31:30,774
Apart from bonus,
what else are your demands?

820
01:31:32,235 --> 01:31:36,181
Sir, bonus is a very old debate.
Since four years.

821
01:31:37,869 --> 01:31:40,202
Government announced to give 8% bonus.

822
01:31:41,590 --> 01:31:45,451
Forget 8%,
owner is not ready to give even 4%.

823
01:31:46,414 --> 01:31:48,576
Seth (Owner) says the
company is running in loss.

824
01:31:48,627 --> 01:31:50,419
It is a lie.
Absolute lie.

825
01:31:50,495 --> 01:31:54,136
Whatever we say and whatever you listen,
will it get published in the paper?

826
01:31:54,812 --> 01:31:56,437
Yes, absolutely.

827
01:31:56,938 --> 01:31:59,271
What will you publish? Nothing.

828
01:32:00,623 --> 01:32:03,460
The mill is owned by a seth,
newspaper of another seth.

829
01:32:03,768 --> 01:32:05,987
What will they publish?
Why will they publish?

830
01:32:06,657 --> 01:32:08,419
What will they publish?

831
01:32:39,323 --> 01:32:40,905
Bring me some food.

832
01:32:46,342 --> 01:32:47,936
Shall we move from here?

833
01:32:49,490 --> 01:32:50,867
What?
- Shall we move?

834
01:32:52,051 --> 01:32:54,212
There is free place there,
if you say, we'll go and sit there.

835
01:32:54,262 --> 01:32:56,137
Shut up, drunkard.

836
01:33:01,549 --> 01:33:03,341
You brought food from home?
- Yes.

837
01:33:04,074 --> 01:33:05,407
Will you have?

838
01:33:05,851 --> 01:33:08,226
I will eat vada pao.
- It is your wish.

839
01:33:26,444 --> 01:33:28,380
Albert, come on,
your customer is here.

840
01:33:28,430 --> 01:33:30,547
Tell him that 15 more minutes
for the lunch break.

841
01:33:30,598 --> 01:33:32,000
Come on, pal. He is your old customer.

842
01:33:32,050 --> 01:33:33,996
Tell him that I will
have food and come.

843
01:33:35,209 --> 01:33:37,883
Okay.. why should I care?
You'll be in loss.

844
01:33:37,978 --> 01:33:39,019
Hey, come on,

845
01:33:39,289 --> 01:33:41,061
Can't you see he is eating.
-Go away.

846
01:33:42,104 --> 01:33:43,354
Strange.

847
01:34:20,941 --> 01:34:22,108
You've reformed.

848
01:35:11,408 --> 01:35:12,491
Stella..

849
01:35:25,365 --> 01:35:26,448
Stella..

850
01:35:27,704 --> 01:35:28,745
Stella..

851
01:35:34,697 --> 01:35:35,822
Stella, I'm sorry.

852
01:35:40,350 --> 01:35:42,603
Actually, that day..

853
01:35:45,127 --> 01:35:46,579
I'm sorry.

854
01:35:56,237 --> 01:35:57,362
Stella, I'm sorry.

855
01:35:59,585 --> 01:36:03,505
Stella, will you marry me?

856
01:36:40,347 --> 01:36:42,374
Daddy..
- Yes.

857
01:36:45,982 --> 01:36:47,232
Cheers.
- Cheers.

858
01:36:51,744 --> 01:36:54,497
In a month or two,
you'll be in Canada.

859
01:36:56,940 --> 01:36:59,231
Did you keep the other papers ready?

860
01:37:00,647 --> 01:37:01,897
Do it today itself.

861
01:37:02,688 --> 01:37:05,605
Post them in the Canadian
embassy tomorrow.

862
01:37:06,345 --> 01:37:07,845
Yeah, I will do all that.

863
01:37:09,151 --> 01:37:10,948
Seems like my thing is sorted.

864
01:37:12,815 --> 01:37:17,689
Look, until your visa doesn't come,
don't tell anyone.

865
01:37:17,775 --> 01:37:19,733
No, no.
- Keep it to yourself.

866
01:37:25,145 --> 01:37:28,373
And yes,
when will you call Alice there?

867
01:37:30,644 --> 01:37:33,227
As soon as I get a job,
Alice will be in Canada.

868
01:37:34,435 --> 01:37:36,102
I don't want to go to Canada.

869
01:37:38,823 --> 01:37:40,989
You don't want to go?
Do you want to rot here?

870
01:37:42,809 --> 01:37:44,184
Are you out of your mind?

871
01:37:44,900 --> 01:37:47,065
Does our people get
any respect in India?

872
01:37:47,237 --> 01:37:48,737
Nobody cares about us.

873
01:37:50,183 --> 01:37:55,635
People are illiterates here..
useless.. good for nothing.

874
01:37:55,870 --> 01:37:58,214
Wherever you go-
there are fights and quarrels.

875
01:37:59,224 --> 01:38:00,516
This place is not ours.

876
01:38:01,641 --> 01:38:03,224
Johnny is right.

877
01:38:04,432 --> 01:38:06,349
India has gone to the shits.

878
01:38:07,556 --> 01:38:10,070
Canada.. now that's a place.

879
01:38:11,253 --> 01:38:14,543
Every person
has first class flat,

880
01:38:14,699 --> 01:38:19,191
car, TV, fridge,
food and drinks..

881
01:38:19,847 --> 01:38:21,180
Everything is A class.

882
01:38:23,430 --> 01:38:24,847
It is a Christian country.

883
01:38:27,388 --> 01:38:29,013
We have some respect there.

884
01:38:36,513 --> 01:38:38,345
We'll know only after we go there.

885
01:38:41,720 --> 01:38:43,476
This is Akashvani Bombay.

886
01:38:43,526 --> 01:38:45,290
Now, you will hear news
from Madhukar Pandey.

887
01:38:45,341 --> 01:38:47,553
The elections of the Colaba district
Panchayat (Village council)

888
01:38:47,603 --> 01:38:49,321
will be held after 2 months.

889
01:38:49,636 --> 01:38:53,511
The governor of Andhra Pradesh,
inaugurated the Filmcity in Hyderabad.

890
01:38:54,011 --> 01:38:56,969
Today is the 15th day of
the cloth mills strike in Bombay.

891
01:38:57,065 --> 01:38:59,463
There has been no resolution
in the talks between

892
01:38:59,514 --> 01:39:01,669
..the labour union
and the owners association.

893
01:39:01,720 --> 01:39:04,042
A spokesperson of the owner's
association told us that..

894
01:39:04,093 --> 01:39:06,868
.. there are batches of laborers
who are now returning to work.

895
01:39:06,939 --> 01:39:11,064
He even said that there are chances of
the strike being called off in few days.

896
01:39:15,342 --> 01:39:17,216
It is a lie.. everything is lie.

897
01:39:17,655 --> 01:39:21,197
What did he say-the spokesperson
at the mill.. he is lying.

898
01:39:21,758 --> 01:39:23,966
He is lying to break our resolve.

899
01:39:34,078 --> 01:39:35,119
Albert..

900
01:39:40,131 --> 01:39:42,589
Until today I didn't tell you
why I am on strike.

901
01:39:44,339 --> 01:39:48,633
It's okay papa..
- I will tell you.. I will tell you.

902
01:39:50,755 --> 01:39:53,234
I have worked for 28 years on
those mill machines.

903
01:39:53,697 --> 01:39:56,369
The noise of the machine
is internalised in my head.

904
01:39:57,227 --> 01:39:59,912
For 28 years I worked
my ass off.

905
01:40:01,223 --> 01:40:04,074
Even when living became
difficult, I stayed silent.

906
01:40:07,169 --> 01:40:08,752
I don't know why I stayed silent.

907
01:40:11,565 --> 01:40:13,307
I had to take care of the family.

908
01:40:16,322 --> 01:40:18,486
I had to raise the children.

909
01:40:20,168 --> 01:40:24,960
Maybe that's why I remained
silent and kept working.

910
01:40:31,171 --> 01:40:33,046
What all we went through..

911
01:40:35,094 --> 01:40:38,134
We didn't get to live with respect
still I remained silent.

912
01:40:40,982 --> 01:40:44,818
Who knows,
maybe I was just a coward.

913
01:40:47,790 --> 01:40:50,998
Owners are not ready to fulfill
even our very small demands.

914
01:40:53,747 --> 01:40:56,913
Now after 28 years,
I have raised my voice.

915
01:40:58,103 --> 01:40:59,686
It is after a long time.

916
01:41:01,254 --> 01:41:03,657
Now I am not going to back down.

917
01:41:05,831 --> 01:41:08,663
I don't know what I will
get by doing strike, but..

918
01:41:09,497 --> 01:41:14,413
..one thing I am sure of
is that I have to fight.

919
01:42:04,408 --> 01:42:07,560
This my chest here na,
cotton has got into it.

920
01:42:09,150 --> 01:42:10,650
There is cotton inside.

921
01:42:11,199 --> 01:42:17,198
The doctor told me that I have
got TB, but I still have to work.

922
01:42:19,488 --> 01:42:22,405
My eyes are just filled
with the mill's smoke.

923
01:42:23,238 --> 01:42:26,738
Wherever I see, I can
just see black.

924
01:42:30,655 --> 01:42:33,186
Till I have these hands,
I have the job,

925
01:42:34,179 --> 01:42:37,279
if it gets severed,
there will be no food.

926
01:42:37,529 --> 01:42:39,404
Do you know the value of this hand?

927
01:42:40,071 --> 01:42:45,695
The hands that work on machine
are worth only Rs. 2000. Rs. 2000.

928
01:42:46,695 --> 01:42:50,075
This is my house.
Everything I have is here.

929
01:42:50,779 --> 01:42:52,987
Eating, sleeping, everything
is here only.

930
01:42:54,403 --> 01:42:57,069
Wherever you see here there's garbage.

931
01:42:58,111 --> 01:43:01,024
Do human beings live like this?

932
01:43:15,755 --> 01:43:17,942
Excuse me,
what is your name?

933
01:43:18,192 --> 01:43:20,109
Ramchander Babbar.
- Where are you from?

934
01:43:20,400 --> 01:43:21,983
Satara. Why?

935
01:43:22,317 --> 01:43:24,567
I was looking for someone.
- Who?

936
01:43:25,150 --> 01:43:26,816
Mohammad Yusuf, Uttar Pradesh.

937
01:43:27,316 --> 01:43:28,608
Ram Singh, Rajasthan.

938
01:43:28,858 --> 01:43:30,399
Ram Sawant, Maharashtra.

939
01:43:30,691 --> 01:43:32,649
Gangaram Chiste, Andhra Pradesh.

940
01:43:32,858 --> 01:43:34,858
Manohar More, Kolhapur.

941
01:43:35,110 --> 01:43:36,526
Bala Unni, Kerala.

942
01:43:37,190 --> 01:43:39,315
Raja Bindeshwari Singh,
Madhya Pradesh.

943
01:43:39,815 --> 01:43:41,065
Venu Gopal, Tamil Nadu.

944
01:43:41,440 --> 01:43:43,315
Rao Bhau Pawar, Maharashtra.

945
01:43:43,607 --> 01:43:45,147
Lakhan Pal, Uttar Pradesh.

946
01:43:45,781 --> 01:43:47,823
Radheshyam Tiwari, Bihar.

947
01:43:48,297 --> 01:43:50,098
Francis Fernandes, Goa.

948
01:43:52,678 --> 01:43:54,280
My name is Albert Pinto.

949
01:44:09,210 --> 01:44:12,502
25th day of strike by the
laborers of Mumbai textile mill.

950
01:44:12,895 --> 01:44:14,687
More than 65 mills are shut.

951
01:44:14,854 --> 01:44:18,240
Chair of the
Bombay millowners association,

952
01:44:18,300 --> 01:44:20,104
Seth Chandumal Podar..

953
01:44:20,186 --> 01:44:22,606
..has opined about the
strike in an interview.

954
01:44:23,091 --> 01:44:27,340
Our country is the biggest sufferer
because of this strike.

955
01:44:28,810 --> 01:44:32,060
The government has incurred
a loss of more than 6 crores.

956
01:44:32,893 --> 01:44:35,559
And at such time, when our country..
- Bloody liar.

957
01:44:35,642 --> 01:44:39,392
..is in dire need
of foreign currency.

958
01:44:42,434 --> 01:44:45,475
We need bread.
- Call it off.

959
01:44:46,766 --> 01:44:50,683
Talk about the countries where
the labor can't go on a strike.

960
01:44:52,308 --> 01:44:55,599
There's so much of
production and happiness.

961
01:44:57,140 --> 01:44:59,015
There should be similar
laws here too.

962
01:44:59,921 --> 01:45:02,233
Then why don't you go there?
- Progress of country..

963
01:45:02,307 --> 01:45:04,599
Why are you dying here?
- Albert!

964
01:45:07,520 --> 01:45:09,145
Who is responsible for the strike?

965
01:45:10,576 --> 01:45:14,323
The leaders of the trade union.
This has become their profession.

966
01:45:16,311 --> 01:45:18,634
We were considering
labourers demands.

967
01:45:19,420 --> 01:45:20,920
We were soon going to decide.

968
01:45:21,722 --> 01:45:23,763
It takes two years to consider?

969
01:45:24,272 --> 01:45:25,272
Hey,

970
01:45:28,215 --> 01:45:30,520
The result... strike.

971
01:45:32,242 --> 01:45:36,307
Ours... country's... labourers...
everyone's loss.

972
01:45:38,345 --> 01:45:40,720
See what all is getting
effected by the strike.

973
01:45:41,970 --> 01:45:45,677
Small scale industries that
are linked to textile mills..

974
01:45:46,010 --> 01:45:47,343
..they are closed down.

975
01:45:47,677 --> 01:45:50,469
Laborers are sitting idle there.
- I see.

976
01:45:50,664 --> 01:45:52,438
He is talking about the laborers now..

977
01:45:52,489 --> 01:45:55,018
Hey, please remain silent.
We have come to see the picture.

978
01:45:55,093 --> 01:45:57,676
You see.. you see.. everyone see it.

979
01:45:57,759 --> 01:45:59,301
Make a fool out of yourself.

980
01:45:59,634 --> 01:46:00,842
Brothers, he is lying.

981
01:46:00,926 --> 01:46:03,006
Shut up.
- What happened to him?

982
01:46:05,383 --> 01:46:08,343
Do you know how much
wage does a mill laborer earn?

983
01:46:13,092 --> 01:46:14,924
Rs. 800.
- All lies!

984
01:46:15,111 --> 01:46:16,541
Hey, shut up.

985
01:46:16,591 --> 01:46:20,799
After working hard for 20 years, do you
know how much a laborer gets? Rs. 800.

986
01:46:20,882 --> 01:46:22,623
Shut up.
- You, shut up.

987
01:46:22,674 --> 01:46:24,548
Hey, enough now. Stay quiet.
- Go out.

988
01:46:24,627 --> 01:46:27,652
Hey, enough is enough.

989
01:46:30,506 --> 01:46:34,838
I think you don't even know
that the laborers who are on strike..

990
01:46:35,547 --> 01:46:39,505
..are taking the help of goons and
stopping the people who want to work.

991
01:46:41,339 --> 01:46:42,880
What nonsense?

992
01:46:42,964 --> 01:46:46,338
Will you stay quiet or not..
- They have hired goons..

993
01:47:10,138 --> 01:47:13,012
How many times should I tell you,
not to allow such people.

994
01:47:13,628 --> 01:47:15,566
I'm telling you, there's still time.

995
01:47:16,242 --> 01:47:18,579
If the labourer leaders accept
their fault.

996
01:47:19,639 --> 01:47:21,139
and call off the strike

997
01:47:21,668 --> 01:47:24,334
..then we will surely
consider laborers demands.

998
01:47:26,292 --> 01:47:29,709
We are not enemies of
the laborers like these leaders.

999
01:47:30,625 --> 01:47:32,375
Laborers are our friends.

1000
01:47:33,625 --> 01:47:35,874
We are partners in progress.

1001
01:49:05,494 --> 01:49:09,941
What makes Albert Pinto angry?

